edu.wpi.cs.wpisuitetng.modules.RequirementsManager.tabs.model

Class Tab

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.wpi.cs.wpisuitetng.modules.RequirementsManager.tabs.model.Tab
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DummyTab

    public class Tab
extends java.lang.Object
    A wrapper class for MainTabView that can be given to components within that view in order to allow them to easily change their titles and icons. Adapted from DummyTab in the project DefectTracker
    Version:
    Mar 17, 2013
    Author:
    Tyler Stone
